data.text:
Kim Kardashian is reportedly seeing Super Bowl winner Odell Beckham Jr, with the pair said to be forming a connection.

Kardashian has been single since August 2022, following the end of a nine-month relationship with Pete Davidson after her divorce from Kanye West.

As for Beckham Jr, he is newly single after breaking up with his long-time partner, Lauren Woods, with whom he has a child.

The Kim Kardashian and Odell Beckham Jr rumors

The latest report, from Gillian Telling of People, suggests that she is getting close with Super Bowl LVI champion, Beckham Jr, who scored a touchdown in the 2021 contest before tearing his ACL.

Kardashian and Beckham Jr are said to be "hanging out" and "making a connection" in what appears to be the talking stage of budding romances.

The 30-year-old would not be the first athlete she's gotten close with, as she previously dated Reggie Bush and Miles Austin of the NFL whilst previously being married to the NBA's Kris Humphries.

Beckham Jr returns to the NFL

Beckham Jr missed the entirety of 2022 after tearing his ACL in the Los Angeles Rams' victory over the Cincinnati Bengals, but is back in the NFL for 2023, having signed with the Baltimore Ravens.

The wide receiver has played two games so far, catching five from seven targets for 66 yards and is yet to score his first touchdown since February 2022, when he earned his first career ring.
